1. Run build/install-deps.sh to install depends.
2. Run make to build
3. Only suppurt build in linux, the Mac maybe suppurt in next.

Build arguments:
  debug=yes build for debug
  libcxx=yes use libc++ as stander library.
So you can run:
  make debug=yes libcxx=yes


